\section{Three-Loop Partial Results}
We include the dominant three-loop corrections to \(\beta_{y_t}\), \(\beta_{g_3}\), and \(\beta_\lambda\) from Chetyrkin et al. (2012) \cite{Chetyrkin2012} and Bednyakov et al. (2014). These shift \(m_H\) by \(\approx -0.25\) GeV, well within the Monte-Carlo uncertainty band.

